ci Fi Channel (United States)|Sci Fi Channel]] for its last five seasons. ''Stargate SG-1'' premiered on Showtime on July 27, 1997; its final episode aired on [[Sky1]] in the United Kingdom on March 13, 2007. ''Stargate SG-1'' was nominated for and won numerous awards in its ten-season run.
